title: Bakgat! (2008) DvDrip - Afrikaans (English subs)
description:
Cast: Ivan Botha, Lelia Etsebeth, Andrew Thompson, Dantus Lundal, Neil Sharam, Ilona Nicholson, Ciska Kruger, Cherie van der Merwe, Altus Theart 
Director: Henk Pretorius 
Screenplay: Henk Pretorius 
Music: Benjamin Willem 
Cinematography: Tom Marais 
Editing: C.A. Van Aswegen 
Sound formats: Dolby Digital, Sony Dynamic Digital Sound, DTS 

The hero is the biggest nerd in school, who naturally has dreams and desires just like any other young man. Things seem to go his way when the rugby captain dumps his girlfriend, the hottest babe around. She picks the nerd as a tool for revenge, seeking to turn him into the rugby captain. This proves more difficult than she thought it would be, but they persevere, making new friends along the way.
